---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="InciKorea — Premium K-Beauty Import Guide">
  <div class="container py-16">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">InciKorea</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Premium K-beauty import guide for the UK & European market</p>
    
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <div style="border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">📋 Regulatory Guide</h2>
        <p>Complete UK compliance framework for importing Korean skincare. SCPN, CPSR, PIF, labelling, and customs requirements.</p>
        <a href="/regulatory-guide" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem;">Read Guide →</a>
      </div>
      
      <div style="border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">📊 Market Analysis</h2>
        <p>CLUNA SWOT analysis, competitor landscape, and UK K-beauty market positioning. Strategic roadmap for market entry.</p>
        <a href="/market-analysis" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem;">Read Analysis →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #f0f7ff; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What is InciKorea?</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"><strong>INCI</strong> stands for <em>International Nomenclature of Cosmetic Ingredients</em> — the global standard for ingredient transparency in cosmetics.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">InciKorea is building premium, ingredient-forward Korean skincare for the UK & European market. We believe in:</p>
      <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <li>Transparency in every product</li>
        <li>Regulatory compliance as standard</li>
        <li>Clinical validation over hype</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Currently:</strong> Launching CLUNA foil mask line with ACC cooling technology. Coming soon to UK retailers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
